Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:29.50,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}星空的彼方 梦的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:33.55,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}让我们拾起攒积放声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:39.35,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}梦所到达的地方 至今仍藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:44.73,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}包裹夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:49.15,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}施起魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:54.57,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}跳出舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:59.87,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}燃烧似的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:04.00,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只是摔一跤的话不会融化消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:05.79,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:10.09,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}拥抱不确定的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:18.05,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}与亘古不变的时间 循着光 迈向前
