Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.61,0:23:34.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\4c&HAE524C&}景色在变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:37.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\4c&HAE524C&}辉煌的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.25,0:23:44.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\4c&HAE524C&}和探寻的珍宝  请永远不要放手
